OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSocial Care: No better time
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto be a care worker, public
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftold                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK government has launched a       
OL,6, campaign to recruit carers in England, 
OL,7, with more than 100,000 roles currently 
OL,8, empty in the sector.                   
OL,10,FThe drive - which will run on          
OL,11,Ftelevision, radio and social media -   
OL,12,Fhighlights the difference care staff   
OL,13,Fcan make to people's lives.            
OL,15,F"There's no better time to become a    
OL,16,Fcare worker," the adverts will say.    
OL,18,FBut care leaders have warned the       
OL,19,Finitiative will not be enough to tackle
OL,20,Fdeep rooted problems in the industry.  
